OL,5, Marks & Spencer has stopped selling    
OL,6, disposable barbecues in its stores     
OL,7, across the UK.                         
OL,9,FThe supermarket said it wanted "to help
OL,10,Fprotect open spaces and reduce the risk
OL,11,Fof fires".                             
OL,13,FLondon Fire Brigade, which has been    
OL,14,Fcalling for a ban on the sale of       
OL,15,Fdisposable barbecues, said the move was
OL,16,F"good news".                           
OL,18,FIt comes after the UK experienced its  
OL,19,Fhottest day ever, with 40C exceeded for
OL,20,Fthe first time.                        
